Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.34,0:00:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess there's no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.29,0:00:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since you've said it, I'll marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuu-chan, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga-chan gave birth to so many puppies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So it was a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though it's finally summer break...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...watching these stupid DVD's gave me a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A future like that is pretty awful even for a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I had a horrible dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You were a dog, and the dog was my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:00:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.40,0:01:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was the worst dream I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A premonition?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That dream is a warning which tells me if I don't have a plan, I would have a terrible future waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, in order to change the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:03:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think one side should fully support the other side starting from the trip tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I understand that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are we playing badminton?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's so that we can decide...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...on the side that's giving support.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Listen, don't ever touch the range.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stir the rice bran once a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and remember to change Inko-chan's water in the morning and at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wrote the rest down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I told you already. I'm going on a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bye, Ya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The weather looks like it'll be good today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be looking forward to your support on that "plan".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, is it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fine, you win! Just get him off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I would've won if that retarded dog wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's probably your punishment for choosing something you're good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously, nothing good ever comes with dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Will it really go smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By the time this trip ends, Minorin and you will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good morning, your timing is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Amazing, simply amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong? You don't look good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}What's wrong with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My, this is a perfect day to set off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Speaking of which, Ami still isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's still some time left before the meet up time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really? Then let's continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's up with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No one is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Y-Yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're two minutes late, Ami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good morning, Amin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're late, stupid Chihuahua.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder where everyone is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, don't run away, you stupid Chihuahua!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ami, we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This tastes awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The plum inside makes it even more awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As expected of Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you want to be my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gosh, you're so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Speaking of which, Aisaka-san isn't here yet, is she late?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun, do you have her contac-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My, the stupid Chihuahua was awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thought you were sleeping with your eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're on a trip, so don't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh yeah, Kawashima, what have you been doing during the summer holidays?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was working the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you started to work again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What about you, Minorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Part-time job, club activities, part-time job, club activities, part-time job, club activities...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...made this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think I just heard "senpai" in a weird voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, supernatural soundtracks from the CD I reserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I'm going to scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisaka, do you like horror in general?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's also unexpected for Kushieda to be afraid of supernatural stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm scared! I'm scared! I'm super scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When I say I'm super scared, \NI mean I'm seriously super scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minorin is really afraid of horror, \Nghosts and supernatural stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why we shall scare Minorin to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then you'll save her, since she would be in despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"I'll protect you, Kushieda", like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the "Scare Minorin, then Prince Charming Will Arrive" plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyway, all scary things are forbidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}God, how long are we going to walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We can see it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Go in and you should be able to go to the balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So this is Ami's villa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are we staying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Correct, Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wow! I'm super grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But we need to clean up the place first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No one has been here since last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}L-Last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:08:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is going to be one long battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since such a beautiful sea is in front of us, just leave cleaning for later on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's right, we'll clean later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What about you, Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why am I cleaning by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This feels so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That looks like a human head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A drowned body!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've touched corpse water!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It seems like they're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You really came, Yuusaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:09:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu came, so as his best friend, I have to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What about the student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ami wants us to buy stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's a motorbike in the warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Motorbike?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take Taiga with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm scared of bikes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You had a chance to be with him alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have my own plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Before they come back, we have to find a possible place to carry out that "plan".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just be honest if you're lovestru-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There was a fly, a fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously, even if she says a possible place...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I should clean this place-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry! I didn't notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll leave immediately...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're pretty daring for coming in while a girl is taking a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-It wasn't on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's fine, I'll keep it a secret from everyone if we do it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you talki-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, don't you want to do it with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Clean the bathtub!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My gosh, what were you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's with that expression? It's priceless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The stupid Chihuahua?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pretending to take a shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Toying around with a guy's pure heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, have you completed the \Ninvestigation on the second floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why you got trolled by the stupid Chihuahua!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fine, I'll check it out myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll teach the stupid Chihuahua a lesson while I'm at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, you stupid Chihuahua!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She was really taking a shower...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The stupid Chihuahua is like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Boing and boing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...and BOING!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cut the pointless crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You bought a lot of stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where's Kitamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He went to park the motorbike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...since you bought everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There was something that touched my... my neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}M-Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Something really touched me just then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's like sticky... It's like seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the smell of seaweed! It's seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It must the ghosts of animals \Nwhich were killed by seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sea otters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It has to be the bodies of sea otters \Nif we're talking about seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A sea otter that's covered with seashells?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is a curse of the sea otters and seaweeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I don't want spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I like it spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How can you eat it if it's not sweet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know, I'll make a sweet-flavored one just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Special treatment for Aisaka-san again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll get hated by other girls like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Including Minori-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did someone call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is it almost done?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It looks pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I just have to put in the curry powder...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, you guys should prepare-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You guys are preparing dinner already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Should I help set the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:12:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuusaku, what's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I heard Takasu's voice, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't know you girls were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Show us your naked body, you narcissist guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop it already...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you saying that? You phony!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not bad, not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I saw a black and hairy thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's probably the ghost of the seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seaweed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuusaku, you're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whatever, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's an evil spirit in this house...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is there something I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Make the curry super spicy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:13:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was kind of rushed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but I made it very spicy as Kushieda wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not as spicy as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga, do you want to try some?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're right, it's not-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In the throat, it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's so spicy that it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's here! It's coming into my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Woah! Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you guys all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's so spicy and delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This certainly has a mysterious drawback...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I feel strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:14:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{while}It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's more if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Refill!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thought I was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay, I'll go clean the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll go with-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was too spicy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I need some medicine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you have a stomachache?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The medicine is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisaka, are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I bought some anti-dyspeptic pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's in my room, do you want to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please take of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wha- Wai-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a chance for you to be alone with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then I'll leave her to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have a stomachache, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because you were dazing off...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll never get tired by looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that a compliment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh right, let's go to the seaside \Nnow if it's all right with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Help me with the glass cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry, what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Enough water?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is it working?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'd feed bad if I saw you in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, do you want to lie down for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're really good at washing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's because I always do it during work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun, that was some amazing curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, you're flattering me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll give you something for helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Keep it a secret from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Does the green tea ice cream good?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It probably tastes average.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are a lot of stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're alone together...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this a chance for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}K-Kushieda, do you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder if the seaweed ghost is still around?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun, have you ever seen ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I believe ghosts exist in this \Nworld, but I've never seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't believe people who said they've seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've also thought about this in the same way:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I believe in the future, I'll fall in love, get married and become happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But actually, I've never had that feeling for anyone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I feel distant to those who talk about love in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's because I can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since ghosts don't exist, I'll never see them, so I'm going to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why my answer to your question is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun, what about you? Can you see ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think I can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why I go to places like supernatural spots and watch horror movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think like this:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When someone who believes in ghosts sees a ghost, they'll get shocked, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are some who will continue to think they don't exist even if they see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but there are also some who will see it because they try their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:19:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why you can't be sure that you'll never see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A UFO?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's probably a satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Satellite...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, I thought it was a UFO.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think it would be great if you can see ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Perhaps there are ghosts that want to be seen by you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why a lot of strange things happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The seaweed ghost was telling that it's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you suddenly saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder when I'll see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's one weird person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji, my stomach doesn't hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:20:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm so full!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why am I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, what should we do tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm talking about our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're making it impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm just supporting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gosh, it's actually so tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thought spending a whole day with Kitamura-kun would be enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But it's giving me a nervous breakdown...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I'm totally fine being with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This house is so big, but we're sitting so close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think it's because we're used to being cramped in a small apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sometimes, I think that dream is kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing, let's go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did I leave my bag in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's sticky...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.41,0:21:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I left it in my bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But it was warm when I touched it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's like someone put it on just then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's something strange with my room, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There were strands of hair on my pillow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What was that-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}N-No, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This has to be a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, this has to be a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a sequel to the doghouse dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then we should wake up if we close our eyes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm scared! I'm scared! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.89,0:23:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm scared of freaky things! I'm scared of ghosts! I'm scared of monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Calm down, Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.04,0:23:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.75,0:23:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm scared of UFO's the most.
